<P>
   &UR; FOR XXXDAY AMs &LR;
</P>
<P>
   Here are today's top news stories from The New York Times News
Service for AMs of Sunday, Aug. 23:
</P>
<P>
   &UR; QUESTIONS OR RERUNS: (888) 346-9867 &LR;
</P>
