in the use of imagery chose this vantage point from which to report
the dramatic story unfolding at 1600 Pennsylvania Avenue. The whole
world was watching . . . and watching . . . and watching as an
historic week of strange events took place in the nation's capital.
A day-by-day recap. (Dart, Cox News Service).
