GEN-CROUSE _ Column. Chris Webber is busted for marijuana. Artie
Ulmer of the Minnesota Vikings is found with the `date rape drug'
in his car. Each tries to blame acquaintances for their illegal
possesions. And that's the trouble with athletes today: they don't
take responsibility for their actions and they're to willing to let
their `friends' take the fall for them. &QL; 
By Karen Crouse. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
