<HEADLINE>
SUN DEVILS SHOW WHY THEY HAVE HIGH HOPES 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By PAOLA BOIVIN  
 c.1998 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   CAMP TONTOZONA, Ariz. _ Just minutes after his team closed camp
with a public scrimmage, Arizona State Coach Bruce Snyder called
his players together.
</P>
<P>
   ``I don't know if you can sense it, but people expect you to be
something special,'' he said.
</P>
